{"type":null,"faqId":7248,"title":"音量调节界面的两种音量指示有什么区别？","answer":"<p>左边的音量指示表示手机的各种提示音，按键音和音乐的大小；<br />右边的音量指示表示来电铃音的大小；<br />需要注意的是通话音量只能在通话时才能调节，平常无法调节；<br />调节的方式是：在通话过程之中按手机左侧的音量控制键。</p>\n<p><img style=\"WIDTH: 282px; HEIGHT: 385px\" alt=\"\" width=\"379\" height=\"564\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/0-111027114701.PNG\" /></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7388","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1319686155000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":248,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}